chatapp.messages.chat

Class Quit

  • java.lang.Object
    • chatapp.messages.chat.Quit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IChatroomMsg, IQuit, IMessage, java.io.Serializable

    public class Quit
extends java.lang.Object
implements IQuit
    This message is sent to a chatroom by a user who wishes to leave the chatroom. The chatroom and all its remote instances should delete that user's IMsgReceiver stub from their copy of the chatroom. Since no information aside from the sender of this message is required, this interface has no methods.
